356
00:16:04,750 --> 00:16:05,630
You passed.

357
00:16:06,390 --> 00:16:07,230
Thanks.

358
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,320
Chen Mo.

359
00:16:16,870 --> 00:16:17,710
Nice!

360
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:20,230
