414
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:10,430
Well.

415
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:11,350
What would you like?

416
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:14,400
I like them all.

417
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:15,750
Let me take a look.

418
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:17,920
