00:19:36,790 --> 00:19:39,110
I think there's a way

427
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:42,720
to solve our issue.

428
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:45,110
But I haven't figured out

429
00:19:45,110 --> 00:19:46,510
how to solve it.

430
00:19:47,070 --> 00:19:48,310
Well, as the saying goes,

431
00:19:48,310 --> 00:19:49,440
