432
00:19:49,990 --> 00:19:51,270
If you're strong, they'll yield.

433
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:52,680
If you're weak, they get stronger.

434
00:19:53,450 --> 00:19:54,310
With great sceneries,

435
00:19:54,310 --> 00:19:56,510
Hangzhou is a perfect place to think.

436
00:19:56,510 --> 00:19:57,880
I'll think about it thoroughly

437
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,000
and come up with a solution.

438
00:19:59,270 --> 00:20:00,110
Boss,

439
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:01,520
don't worry.

440
00:20:01,530 --> 00:20:03,000
Stop doing this.

441
00:20:03,270 --> 00:20:04,110
I...

442
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:06,110
