I bought a new one.

444
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:07,940
It will arrive in a few days.

445
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:09,160
It can be repaired.

446
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:10,550
Please don't. Don't want it.

447
00:20:10,550 --> 00:20:11,680
I've already bought it.

448
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:13,200
It'll arrive soon, and I...

449
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,160
Mr. Zhang.

450
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,590
Have you decided?

451
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:19,480
I... I'll have...

452
00:20:20,070 --> 00:20:20,910
have...

453
00:20:21,350 --> 00:20:22,190
have...

454
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:23,080
have...

455
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:24,310
Pork chop noodles?

456
00:20:25,180 --> 00:20:26,390
No, I'll have...

457
00:20:26,830 --> 00:20:27,960
Wontons?

458
00:20:28,590 --> 00:20:29,510
I can't order now.

459
00:20:29,790 --> 00:20:31,510
I just got a call.

460
00:20:31,510 --> 00:20:32,640
I'm going to Hangzhou.

461
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:35,480
Call me if anything comes up.

462
00:20:35,750 --> 00:20:36,960
Then why were you pretending

463
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:38,000
to make orders?

464
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,880
Are you playing me?

465
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,750
So what if I did?

466
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:44,480
It'll collapse.

467
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,030
The wonderful

468
00:20:46,030 --> 00:20:47,240
image of you in my heart

469
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:48,480
just collapsed!

470
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:50,200
You are so dramatic.

471
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,510
Zhang Qiming, you...

472
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:56,280
How ridiculous.

473
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:03,110
Why is the midterm exam
coming up so soon?

474
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:05,160
It feels like school just started.

475
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:06,590
Yes.

476
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:08,160
High school is just one exam

477
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,640
after another exam.

478
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:11,910
Qian Jiayue.

479
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:13,800
Mao Tou?

480
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:14,840
Why are you here?

481
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,000
Emergency.

482
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,480
What emergency?

483
00:21:19,960 --> 00:21:20,880
You have to save me.

484
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:24,390
Report.

485
00:21:29,070 --> 00:21:30,110
Jiayue.

486
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:32,550
Why is it you again?

487
00:21:34,270 --> 00:21:35,160
This time,

488
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:37,510
Zhang Yang made

489
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:38,920
a serious mistake

490
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:40,440
and unforgivable mistake.

491
00:21:40,550 --> 00:21:41,390
Do you understand?

492
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,510
You're only his neighbor.

493
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:43,510
You're not responsible.

494
00:21:43,510 --> 00:21:45,440
What did he do this time?

495
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:46,280
Cheating.

496
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:48,510
Group cheating!

497
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:50,350
I caught them in the act.

498
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:51,350
It was his idea.

499
00:21:51,550 --> 00:21:53,510
I asked others to call their parents.

500
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:54,960
They came immediately,

501
00:21:54,960 --> 00:21:56,160
but he played tricks again

502
00:21:56,160 --> 00:21:57,400
and called you over.

503
00:21:57,550 --> 00:21:58,550
Listen,

504
00:21:58,550 --> 00:22:00,590
you're definitely getting expelled.

505
00:22:00,590 --> 00:22:01,590
