506
00:22:01,590 --> 00:22:02,430
Mr. Jiang!

507
00:22:03,390 --> 00:22:05,240
Please give him another chance.

508
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:06,790
I'll vouch for him.

509
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:08,720
His dad is really busy.

510
00:22:08,830 --> 00:22:10,400
He's often on business trips.

511
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:12,200
I assure you,

512
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,550
as soon as he's back,

513
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:14,990
I'll take him to school

514
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,160
right away.

515
00:22:21,690 --> 00:22:22,530
Goodbye.

516
00:22:23,270 --> 00:22:24,510
Why are you saying goodbye?

517
00:22:26,330 --> 00:22:27,170
I'm going home.

518
00:22:27,390 --> 00:22:28,680
For what?

519
00:22:28,960 --> 00:22:29,840
Your dad isn't there.

520
00:22:29,850 --> 00:22:31,110
What are you going to eat?

521
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:34,790
Don't tell them about this.

522
00:22:41,550 --> 00:22:42,440
Mao Tou.

523
00:22:42,950 --> 00:22:44,350
You're already in Grade 9.

524
00:22:44,490 --> 00:22:45,880
Can't you focus on your studies?

525
00:22:46,310 --> 00:22:47,160
Look at you.

526
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,160
School just started,

527
00:22:48,160 --> 00:22:49,320
and you're already in trouble.

528
00:22:49,830 --> 00:22:51,000
Listen,

529
00:22:51,350 --> 00:22:53,270
Zombie is targeting me on purpose.

530
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:54,680
He's Mr. Jiang.

531
00:22:54,680 --> 00:22:56,480
Don't give teachers nicknames.

532
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:01,520
Anybody home?

533
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:03,880
- Who?
- Anybody...?

534
00:23:03,880 --> 00:23:05,550
Is Guan Aiping home?

535
00:23:11,440 --> 00:23:12,280
Hello.

536
00:23:12,300 --> 00:23:13,150
Hello.

537
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:14,550
Is this Guan Aiping's home?

538
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:15,800
Yes.

539
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:16,920
What do you need?

540
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:18,590
We're delivering a washing machine.

541
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:19,880
Come on, bring it in.

542
00:23:20,020 --> 00:23:20,860
Come on.

543
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:22,590
Wait a minute.

544
00:23:22,810 --> 00:23:23,920
Who bought this?

545
00:23:24,110 --> 00:23:25,480
There's an order.

546
00:23:26,290 --> 00:23:27,130
Mr. Zhang

547
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:28,940
asked us to deliver it here.

548
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:30,580
(Zhang Qiming)
Room 207, right?

549
00:23:30,580 --> 00:23:31,420
Yes.

550
00:23:32,310 --> 00:23:33,150
Right here.

551
00:23:33,740 --> 00:23:35,310
This isn't ours. Please take it back.

552
00:23:35,310 --> 00:23:36,510
Wait a moment, young man.

553
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:38,070
How's that possible?

554
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:39,790
The order says Room 207, right?

555
00:23:39,790 --> 00:23:40,720
This is your place.

556
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:42,030
I said it's not ours.

557
00:23:42,160 --> 00:23:43,110
Take it back. Return it.

558
00:23:43,320 --> 00:23:44,480
- Wait!
- Hey, buddy.

559
00:23:44,480 --> 00:23:45,680
- You can't.
- Can't return it.

560
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:46,590
Mr. Zhang

561
00:23:46,590 --> 00:23:48,620
opened the package in our store.

562
00:23:48,620 --> 00:23:49,500
It's brand new.

563
00:23:49,500 --> 00:23:50,680
- Why can't I return it?
- No...

564
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:52,110
Young man, don't rush.

565
00:23:52,590 --> 00:23:54,160
We're just delivery guys.

566
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:55,510
We deliver the washing machine

567
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:57,590
and test the water connections,

568
00:23:57,590 --> 00:23:58,830
and our job is done.

569
00:23:59,000 --> 00:23:59,880
If you don't want it,

570
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:01,070
throw it away

571
00:24:01,070 --> 00:24:02,160
or give it

572
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,510
to a garbageman.

573
00:24:03,510 --> 00:24:05,070
It's none of our business, okay?

574
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:06,920
We're just trying to make a living.

575
00:24:06,920 --> 00:24:08,880
Young man, please help us.

576
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:10,310
Don't make it hard for us, alright?

577
00:24:10,310 --> 00:24:11,310
Okay? Please help us.

578
00:24:11,510 --> 00:24:12,350
Yes.

579
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:16,310
Okay, where should I put it?

580
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,270
- Bathroom.
- Okay, bathroom.

581
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:19,750
Put it properly.

582
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:21,070
- Okay?
- Okay.

583
00:24:24,750 --> 00:24:26,000
Do you know this place?

584
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:28,510
