00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,140
We can even watch movies there.

587
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:33,350
Mao Tou.

588
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:36,720
Come over.

589
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:40,510
Your parents

590
00:24:40,750 --> 00:24:43,000
had their first date here.

591
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:45,070
Later on,

592
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:48,110
(Employee Canteen)
they often brought you here to have meals

593
00:24:48,110 --> 00:24:49,480
and watch movies.

594
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,310
It was really interesting.

595
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,440
Granny, is this you?

596
00:24:55,510 --> 00:24:56,350
Yes, it is.

597
00:24:57,200 --> 00:24:58,750
Comrade Liao Dongmei,

598
00:24:58,750 --> 00:25:00,240
March 8th Red Flag Bearer.

599
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:01,960
Granny, you used to be

600
00:25:01,960 --> 00:25:03,160
a March 8th Red Flag Bearer?

601
00:25:03,550 --> 00:25:05,000
Flag bearer of Shanghai City.

602
00:25:05,160 --> 00:25:06,510
That was a big title.

603
00:25:08,270 --> 00:25:11,030
(Puyang No. 9 Cotton Textile Factory)
Look, many model workers' names

604
00:25:11,030 --> 00:25:12,400
(List of Model Workers)
are here.

605
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:13,560
Isn't it great?

606
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:16,160
Model workers?

607
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:18,160
Now they're all laid-off workers.

608
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:20,110
Don't put it like that,

609
00:25:20,110 --> 00:25:20,950
okay?

610
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:24,030
Time only moves forward indeed,

611
00:25:24,790 --> 00:25:26,550
but we should respect history
all the same.

612
00:25:29,110 --> 00:25:31,070
We should especially respect

613
00:25:31,310 --> 00:25:34,110
the honorable traditions and history

614
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:35,680
of hard-working workers.

615
00:25:37,720 --> 00:25:38,560
Shouldn't we?

616
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,040
- Yes.
- Yes.

617
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:41,880
But now,

618
00:25:42,880 --> 00:25:44,030
look at all these

619
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:46,000
articles and TV series.

620
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:47,790
Whenever it comes to Shanghai,

621
00:25:47,790 --> 00:25:49,920
it's always about old Shanghai,

622
00:25:50,270 --> 00:25:52,310
the decadent music,

623
00:25:52,310 --> 00:25:53,200
and the Paramount.

624
00:25:53,250 --> 00:25:54,110
No, that's not right.

625
00:25:54,110 --> 00:25:54,950
Absolutely not.

626
00:25:57,510 --> 00:25:58,350
Do you know

627
00:25:59,310 --> 00:26:00,550
what Shanghai is?

628
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:03,000
It's where I grew up.

629
00:26:07,550 --> 00:26:11,310
It's also the birthplace
of the modern labor movement.

630
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,070
This time, Dong and others

631
00:26:13,070 --> 00:26:14,510
not only established a museum,

632
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:16,350
but also made a brochure.

633
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:18,680
That's how we respect history.

634
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:20,270
Everyone who worked

635
00:26:20,270 --> 00:26:22,110
at No. 9 Factory

636
00:26:22,750 --> 00:26:24,070
can savor the old days.

637
00:26:25,270 --> 00:26:26,110
Good on them.

638
00:26:26,510 --> 00:26:29,000
Please move forward.

639
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,270
The factory is closed,

640
00:26:31,270 --> 00:26:33,070
and we've got the compensation.

641
00:26:33,070 --> 00:26:34,790
What's the point of establishing

642
00:26:35,110 --> 00:26:36,110
a museum?

643
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:39,310
Anyway, I won't go to
the opening ceremony.

644
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,960
For people like you,

645
00:26:41,070 --> 00:26:43,110
I know you won't be there.

646
00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:44,720
But I'll definitely attend it.

647
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:46,000
Go if you will,

648
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:49,160
but don't drag Aiping along.

649
00:26:49,930 --> 00:26:52,510
I'm worried she'll feel upset

650
00:26:52,790 --> 00:26:54,070
when she visits the old place.

651
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,310
Sometimes, I think

652
00:26:58,310 --> 00:27:00,110
Xiao Youguang was quite silly.

653
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:03,160
He sacrificed his life heroically,

654
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:06,000
but left a widow and a child behind.

655
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,160
All his efforts in vain.

656
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:10,240
Don't talk nonsense
in front of the kids.

657
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:11,400
How's that nonsense?

658
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:13,310
I'm just telling the truth, right?

659
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:15,110
Look at Aiping.

660
00:27:15,270 --> 00:27:16,790
She has two jobs.

661
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:18,070
She works from 5 a.m.

662
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:20,000
to 9 p.m. at night.

663
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:21,720
As for Xiao Han,

664
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:23,070
he grew up without a father.

665
00:27:23,610 --> 00:27:24,450
Poor child.

666
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:26,070
His clothes

667
00:27:26,070 --> 00:27:27,070
and backpacks

668
00:27:27,070 --> 00:27:28,750
are all hand-me-downs.

669
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:31,070
Poor boy.

670
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:35,640
Now, look at Mao Tou.

671
00:27:36,440 --> 00:27:38,720
Mao Tou, your dad was a nobody

672
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:40,510
at No. 9 Factory.

673
00:27:41,350 --> 00:27:43,000
But now he's quite something.

674
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:44,400
Style his hair,

675
00:27:44,510 --> 00:27:45,750
hold a cell phone,

676
00:27:45,750 --> 00:27:48,550
ride in a car. He's a boss now.

677
00:27:51,510 --> 00:27:52,790
As for Xiao Youguang,

678
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:56,790
who still remembers him?

679
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:59,070
No one.

680
00:27:59,550 --> 00:28:01,000
Whether he's remembered or not,

681
00:28:01,110 --> 00:28:02,400
Xiao Youguang is always a hero.

682
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:04,880
Nowadays, if you can make money,
you'll be a hero.

683
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:05,910
Mom!

684
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:07,200
Please stop!

685
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:08,510
I don't want to hear it!

686
00:28:17,070 --> 00:28:18,070
I'm back.

687
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:20,510
Mom, you're back.

688
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:29,800
Mom.

689
00:28:35,750 --> 00:28:36,960
He sent it to us.

690
00:28:40,110 --> 00:28:40,950
Han.

691
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,270
Mom didn't accept it.

692
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:43,480
I know.

693
00:28:44,550 --> 00:28:45,390
Mom.

694
00:28:45,510 --> 00:28:46,350
Don't use it now.

695
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:48,200
I'll find a way to return it.

696
00:28:49,110 --> 00:28:50,550
Then I'll buy you a new one

697
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:51,590
with my own money.

698
00:28:52,590 --> 00:28:53,920
How will you get the money?

699
00:28:56,590 --> 00:28:59,640
(Self-Reliance Scholarship Application:
No poor student should be left behind)

700
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:09,580
(Xiao Han)
Scholarship.

701
00:29:12,030 --> 00:29:12,870
Mom.

702
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:14,510
Without others' help,

703
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:16,350
I can give you a good life.

704
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:40,550
Why were you drunk again?

705
00:29:40,550 --> 00:29:41,750
Didn't you go to Hangzhou?

706
00:29:42,860 --> 00:29:47,160
When you say Hangzhou,
I go to Hangzhou.

707
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:50,510
If you say Shanghai,
I go to Shanghai.

708
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:53,110
Anywhere in the world.
Who am I?

709
00:29:53,110 --> 00:29:54,270
I'm Zhang Qiming.

710
00:29:54,830 --> 00:29:56,830
When you call, I'll come. When I come,

711
00:30:03,950 --> 00:30:04,790
I'll drink.

712
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:10,680
Feeling better?

713
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:12,920
I'm fine.

714
00:30:13,590 --> 00:30:14,590
Let's head back.

715
00:30:20,880 --> 00:30:21,720
Son.

716
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:25,510
Listen, I'm really struggling.

717
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:28,560
Because...

718
00:30:30,360 --> 00:30:32,510
nobody respects me.

719
00:30:34,310 --> 00:30:35,150
Yang Min.

720
00:30:37,510 --> 00:30:38,400
Be careful.

721
00:30:49,510 --> 00:30:50,880
Yang Min...

722
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:52,200
Come on, rinse your mouth.

723
00:30:52,350 --> 00:30:53,960
She's not worthy to be your mom.

724
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:55,920
She looked down on me.

725
00:31:03,510 --> 00:31:06,110
She went to Japan and left us behind.

726
00:31:06,110 --> 00:31:07,160
She looked down on me.

727
00:31:09,510 --> 00:31:10,960
She's not worthy to be your mom.

728
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:15,920
Are you finished?

729
00:31:17,720 --> 00:31:18,750
Yes.

730
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:20,270
Alright. Don't worry about that.

731
00:31:20,270 --> 00:31:21,310
Let's go.

732
00:31:21,830 --> 00:31:22,670
Come on.

733
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:26,840
Mao Tou.

734
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:30,070
I must show everyone

735
00:31:31,070 --> 00:31:32,510
I am a role model.

736
00:31:32,510 --> 00:31:33,350
Okay.

737
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:36,070
Not in the bedroom.

738
00:31:36,070 --> 00:31:37,590
It's hard to clean.

739
00:31:38,070 --> 00:31:38,910
Let's go outside.

740
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:41,070
You're my son.

741
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:41,910
Yes.

742
00:31:42,400 --> 00:31:43,750
You're also a role model.

743
00:31:43,750 --> 00:31:44,590
Yes.

744
00:31:46,070 --> 00:31:47,070
Slow down, careful.

745
00:31:47,070 --> 00:31:48,310
Never mess up.

746
00:31:48,310 --> 00:31:49,400
I won't mess up.

747
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,510
Keep it in mind.

748
00:31:51,510 --> 00:31:52,590
Alright, alright.

749
00:31:53,510 --> 00:31:55,000
Over here, this way.

750
00:31:57,180 --> 00:31:58,070
Come on, come on.

751
00:31:58,070 --> 00:31:59,590
Never mess up.

752
00:31:59,590 --> 00:32:00,720
Be careful.

753
00:32:51,940 --> 00:32:55,020
(First Canteen)

754
00:33:07,100 --> 00:33:09,020
(Class 5, Grade 10)

755
00:33:10,350 --> 00:33:11,590
Some groups haven't given

756
00:33:11,590 --> 00:33:13,000
the lunch money for next month.

757
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,310
Hurry up, everyone!

758
00:33:15,310 --> 00:33:16,160
How many groups?

759
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,240
Only two groups left.

760
00:33:18,510 --> 00:33:19,920
It's time for the P.E. class.

761
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:27,350
- Alright.
- Finished?

762
00:33:28,110 --> 00:33:29,590
- Let's go.
- It's really

763
00:33:29,590 --> 00:33:31,400
an ordinary pair of sneakers.

764
00:33:31,720 --> 00:33:33,070
Can't compare to your Air Jordans.

765
00:33:33,390 --> 00:33:34,940
- It's really...
- New shoes, Wang Bin.

766
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:36,280
You noticed?

767
00:33:37,030 --> 00:33:37,880
According to the rule,

768
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:39,510
we should step on them.

769
00:33:39,510 --> 00:33:40,830
Don't! You'll ruin them!

770
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,320
Chang Wuji!

771
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:45,760
You go first.

772
00:33:48,310 --> 00:33:49,590
Why did she take the initiative?

773
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:52,720
The school magazine is soliciting
articles about good students.

774
00:33:52,960 --> 00:33:56,160
Qian Jiayue decided
to write an exclusive interview for this.

775
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:58,720
She's creating trouble for herself.

776
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:03,350
Why do I like science subjects?

777
00:34:04,790 --> 00:34:07,350
Why are you asking me this?

778
00:34:08,740 --> 00:34:09,920
(Integrity, Diligence,
Responsibility, Virtue)

779
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,400
It's Zhao Tingting again.

780
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:13,840
(Zhao Tingting, Xiao Han)
She's next to Xiao Han.

781
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:17,180
(Striving)

782
00:34:19,550 --> 00:34:20,480
Here's the thing.

783
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:23,040
I want to write an article
about an interesting classmate

784
00:34:23,190 --> 00:34:25,000
for the school magazine.

785
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:26,160
Me?

786
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:28,550
You think I'm interesting?

787
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:32,360
Actually, I just want to ask

788
00:34:32,670 --> 00:34:34,320
if you find math

789
00:34:34,550 --> 00:34:36,110
and physics interesting?

790
00:34:36,110 --> 00:34:38,150
I do find them quite interesting.

791
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,840
Well, for example,

792
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:42,280
what's interesting about them?

793
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:43,510
Fibonacci sequence.

794
00:34:45,710 --> 00:34:47,150
It's a sequence

795
00:34:47,160 --> 00:34:48,710
of natural numbers,

796
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,630
yet its formula

797
00:34:50,640 --> 00:34:52,150
involves irrational numbers.

798
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:54,440
Moreover, as it approaches infinity,

799
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:55,630
the ratio of consecutive terms

800
00:34:55,630 --> 00:34:57,320
gets closer to 0.618.

801
00:34:57,920 --> 00:34:59,400
It's the golden ratio.

802
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:05,240
Cool.

803
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:08,870
By the way,

804
00:35:09,080 --> 00:35:11,110
how did the genius interview go?

805
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:13,190
I didn't understand a thing.

806
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:15,400
No wonder he's a genius.

807
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:18,230
But why did you suddenly
want to write for the magazine?

808
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:20,280
Well...

809
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:21,550
Since

810
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:23,670
the class placement exam,

811
00:35:23,840 --> 00:35:24,680
she's been down

812
00:35:24,690 --> 00:35:26,550
because she couldn't make it
to the key class.

813
00:35:27,480 --> 00:35:30,190
I guess she wants to prove herself
in another way.

814
00:35:30,510 --> 00:35:32,400
Prove herself?

815
00:35:32,710 --> 00:35:34,840
She just wants
to create more opportunities

816
00:35:34,840 --> 00:35:36,840
to get closer to someone.

817
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:38,160
Nonsense.

818
00:35:39,110 --> 00:35:40,670
Ka Men, can I borrow your notes?

819
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:41,800
Get it yourself.

820
00:35:42,150 --> 00:35:43,270
Pass it, please.

821
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:44,600
Okay.

822
00:35:45,150 --> 00:35:46,840
Gone, it's all gone!

823
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:48,400
What's gone?

824
00:35:48,920 --> 00:35:49,960
The lunch money is gone!

825
00:35:50,910 --> 00:35:51,890
Lunch money?

826
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:54,230
Take everything out.

827
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:56,440
I remember I put it in the drawer.

828
00:35:56,630 --> 00:35:58,150
Yes, we all saw that.

829
00:35:58,150 --> 00:35:59,550
Yes. How could it be missing?

830
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:00,920
Who took the lunch money?

831
00:36:00,920 --> 00:36:02,010
Give it back!

832
00:36:03,510 --> 00:36:04,350
Qian Jiayue.

833
00:36:05,150 --> 00:36:06,150
Is the money missing?

834
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:09,680
I'm sorry...

835
00:36:10,150 --> 00:36:11,710
How could you be so careless?

836
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:13,190
It's not her fault.

837
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:14,760
I saw her put it in the drawer

838
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:16,400
before the P.E. class,

839
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:18,550
and she tied a knot on the bag.

840
00:36:18,630 --> 00:36:19,670
I saw it too.

841
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:21,880
Who took the lunch money?

842
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:23,710
It was lost during the P.E. class.

843
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:25,320
Maybe it wasn't our classmate.

844
00:36:25,550 --> 00:36:27,030
Only our classmates knew

845
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:28,390
we collected lunch money today.

846
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:29,600
Yes, that's right.

847
00:36:30,230 --> 00:36:31,630
Others didn't know

848
00:36:31,630 --> 00:36:32,670
Qian Jiayue had the money.

849
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:35,280
Well,

850
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:38,550
who went back during the P.E. class?

851
00:36:39,150 --> 00:36:39,990
Yes.

852
00:36:40,030 --> 00:36:40,960
Who came back?

853
00:36:41,110 --> 00:36:42,230
No one came back.

854
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:47,200
Time to go.

855
00:37:01,550 --> 00:37:02,390
Wait.

856
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:04,360
Why's everyone looking at me?

857
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:06,550
I did come back,

858
00:37:06,550 --> 00:37:07,760
I needed to grab something.

859
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,510
What did you grab?

860
00:37:10,550 --> 00:37:11,760
What do you mean, Chen Mo?

861
00:37:12,590 --> 00:37:13,960
You think I took it, huh?

862
00:37:14,710 --> 00:37:16,630
My new basketball shoes

863
00:37:16,630 --> 00:37:17,920
were stepped on.

864
00:37:18,710 --> 00:37:19,920
I felt bad,

865
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:20,960
so I changed them.

866
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:21,800
What's wrong?

867
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:23,160
Is there a problem?

868
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:24,760
You came back too.

869
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:26,320
She also came back.

870
00:37:26,320 --> 00:37:27,750
I went to the bathroom.

871
00:37:27,840 --> 00:37:29,590
Besides,
how could I take Jiayue's money?

